sc101-nbd (0.05) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
  * Add LSB-compliant init.d script for the Debian package.
  * Switch to git(1) as version control system.
  * Include <limits.h> since we need PATH_MAX. This fixes a compilation error
    on Ubuntu 10.10.
  * Minor changes:
      - Add README.
      - Eliminate warnings about ignored return values.
      - Whitespace cleanup.

 -- Claudio Jolowicz <cj@dealloc.org>  Fri, 11 Feb 2011 17:10:05 +0100

